second half of 1992 than in the first half, excluding the impact of special
items.
On Tuesday, USX announced second-quarter net income of Dollars 226m for its
Marathon business and Dollars 6m for its US Steel group. The Marathon
figures included a Dollars 119m tax refund.
Mr Corry told a news conference that the steel side, which was hard-hit by
