the largest operators in the national market.
Garma, a holding company controlled by Mr Gardini, has paid an undisclosed
sum to an Italian businessman for Italfin, a drinks business with a combined
annual mineral water turnover equivalent to Dollars 200m.
This is Mr Gardini's second Italian mineral water acquisition within a
fortnight and lifts his market share to 20 per cent, where he rivals the
