when others buy blind.'
The group increased its cash by about Pounds 1m to Pounds 8m, giving the
opportunity to selectively acquire 'good, well-run companies which are now
cheaper than they were a few years ago'.
Earnings per share expanded to 8.59p (6.82p).
The interim dividend is raised from 1.15p to 1.32p.
