FT  31 JUL 92 / Snub for NUJ
</HEADLINE>
<TEXT>
THE Daily Telegraph yesterday derecognised the National Union of Journalists
 -the third national newspaper publisher to do so.
</TEXT>
<PUB>The Financial Times
</PUB>
<PAGE>
London Page 6
