appointed marketing and merchandise director of POUNDSTRETCHER, an operating
subsidiary of Brown &amp; Jackson. Pat Lofthouse, formerly with Hull Health
Authority, joins as human resources director, and Steve Rossi, who has been
working with the company as a part-time consultant, joins as development
director.
