           Revenue          %     profit       %      Net        %
Company       (Ybn)    change     (Ybn)   change   profit   change
Asahi        357.2       9.6       7.9     -8.5      3.1      0.9
Sapporo      246.8       2.7       4.6     22.5      2.1    -29.2
